{"id": "1447417085188771861", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 19, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "I just noticed there was a split I missed in the middle of what I thought was the Celestial Aria chunk. Gonna split those here into:\n\n- First 3:\n```Message from Afar\nKeep@2... Keeper...\nYou feel smothered and shrouded, as if layers of thick velvet fabric press down upon you. You cannot see or move.\n```\n- Last 3:\n```Your consciousness has reached its limit, Tohuwabohu... Now, return to your slumber!\nYou rally your almost exhausted spirit, infusing the last mental strength into your Silver Key.\nGrasping the silver light like a blade, you stab it toward the god before you—\n```\n- Is this ALL of `Celestial Aria`?\n\n\n- First 3:\n```Welcome back, partner.\nUnknowingly, Misag Square was arranged for a small tea party, and Ramona was standing by a little table full of muffins, jams, and tea, smiling and reaching out to you.\nI wonder if I have the honor to invite you to the return tea party we prepared for you?\n```\n- Last 3:\n```Of course, because as Tawil once said, I am the variable of this world, the future of this world.\nAs your words were spoken, the door to the laboratory slowly opened. The outside air and sunlight gradually fell on you, like a silent greeting or a response.\nThis world is waiting for you, waiting for the changes you are about to bring, the future you are about to create.\n```\n- What is this the beginning and end of?", "timestamp": "2025-12-08T02:38:44.818000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1447369074261626981", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
